.SS DESCRIPTION
The \f[B]\-\-buffers\f[R] flag allows you to configure the sizes of the
buffers used by tracee.
.PP
Buffer sizes for perf ring buffers (kernel\-events, kernel\-blob,
control\-plane\-events) are specified in pages.
The pipeline buffer size is specified in event objects.
The default size for perf ring buffers is 1024 pages.
The default size for the pipeline buffer is 10000 event objects.
.PP
