\f[B]kernel\-events=<size>\f[R]: Sets the size, in pages, of the
internal perf ring buffer used to submit events from the kernel.
.IP \[bu] 2
\f[B]kernel\-blob=<size>\f[R]: Sets the size, in pages, of the internal
perf ring buffer used to send blobs from the kernel.
.IP \[bu] 2
\f[B]control\-plane\-events=<size>\f[R]: Sets the size, in pages, of the
internal perf ring buffer used to submit events from the control plane.
.IP \[bu] 2
\f[B]pipeline=<size>\f[R]: Sets the size, in event objects, of each
pipeline stage\[cq]s output channel.
